name: Overgrowth 0.00
description:
This is the 0.00 ver. of the game Overgrowth made for the yume nikki dream diary jam 2.

Graphics and pictures are by Rpg maker and myself.

Characters are by myself, and my friends. 

Characters so far:

Pumpkin(By me), Nurses(By me),Ori(By me), Peanut(By me), Gumball(By my friend  fc), Chico(By my friend Royce), Siren(By my friend SirensSilence) Bri(By my friend Bri)

There are no other characters.

There are 4 effects to find.

Enjoy.

If the download doesn't work you can download it from here:
